  "body": "## What's New\n\n* **Move VM Feature**: You can now move an existing Virtual Machine to a different folder/drive from the UI. The backend handles `tree.dat` snapshot rebasing automatically.\n* **ApiValidator Bypass**: Fixed the `ApiValidator` error (exit code 193) for `AppSandboxVAD.vcxproj`.\n* **PowerShell 7 Pipeline Upgrade**: Switched signing tasks from `powershell` to `pwsh` to fix `FormatXmlUpdateException` failures during GitHub Actions builds.\n* **WDK Caching**: Implemented WDK caching on GitHub Actions, cutting environment setup time significantly.\n\n**Full Changelog**: https://github.com/bruhmomentumtr/appsandbox/commits/v0.13"
